        "Clean card surfaces with subtle 1px borders rather than heavy drop shadows",
        "Gradient overlay technique used on poster block images"
      ],
      "from_reference_3_desktop_saas": [
        "Fixed left sidebar with section labels in uppercase small caps",
        "Date-column (fixed width) + events-column (flex) split layout for desktop feed",
        "Large date number (2xl Syne) paired with day name (xs caps muted) in date column",
        "Event rows separated by subtle bottom border rather than card elevation",
        "Left accent bar on rows using category color — 3px, vertically centered",
        "Inline meta row pattern — organizer, time, venue with small icons on one line",
        "Right panel for detail view — fixed width, activated on row click"
